{"id":"C9zCh580qaElODp0","meta":{"instanceId":"8443f10082278c46aa5cf3acf8ff0f70061a2c58bce76efac814b16290845177","templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"name":"AI Citation Monitoring & Brand Visibility Analytics System","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"394e1942-6564-47d2-a4ef-11a42aa3ec89","name":"📌 Overview – How This Workflow Works","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-240,-592],"parameters":{"width":700,"height":512,"content":"## 📊 Fairy Frills – AI Citation Monitoring\n\n### How it works\nThis workflow runs every week and checks whether fairyfrills.in gets cited as a source when AI models answer shopping queries about baby and kids fashion in India. Fifteen queries go to two OpenAI models in parallel — one using static training knowledge, one browsing the live web. A citation extractor then pulls every URL referenced in each response, identifies whether your domain appeared, and notes the surrounding context.\n\nResults are logged to a Google Sheet row by row. After the 15th query, the workflow fetches the week's data and sends an HTML report covering citation rate, which pages were cited, how competitors compared, and which queries represent content gaps to fill.\n\n### Setup steps\n1. Add your **OpenAI API** credential to all three OpenAI nodes.\n2. Create a Google Sheet with a tab named **Citation Log** — add the column headers listed in the Log node's field mapping.\n3. Replace `YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID` in both Google Sheets nodes with your actual Sheet ID.\n4. Connect **Gmail OAuth2** to the email report node and update the recipient address.\n5. Optionally connect **Slack OAuth2** and replace `YOUR_SLACK_CHANNEL_ID` for error alerts.\n6. Activate the Weekly Schedule Trigger."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"58650488-107f-4b73-a821-3a041c486452","name":"Section – Trigger & Query Generation","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[320,128],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":580,"height":300,"content":"## ⏰ Trigger & Query Generation\nFires once a week and outputs 15 shopping queries pre-loaded with the target domain, brand name, and competitor list. Every downstream node receives this context without additional configuration."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"1d3a2653-4911-4725-93d9-c806e6ceb465","name":"Section – Parallel AI Queries","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[912,-80],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":420,"height":664,"content":"## 🤖 Parallel AI Queries\ngpt-4o-mini answers from training data; gpt-4o-search-preview browses the live web and includes source URLs. Running them in parallel reveals the difference between static and real-time citation coverage for your domain."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"f926253b-75f7-4869-a625-4bfca060edbf","name":"Section – Merge & Citation Extraction","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1360,-96],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":788,"height":666,"content":"## 🔬 Merge & Citation Extraction\nCombines both AI responses into one item per query, then a citation-focused prompt extracts every URL referenced — identifying your domain's position, anchor context, and competitor citations. Temperature is 0 for consistent extraction."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"2482a066-f376-47d4-8fe6-0cedd0791075","name":"Section – Logging & Weekly Report","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[2176,-80],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":1360,"height":666,"content":"## 📝 Logging & Weekly Report\nParses the citation JSON, maps fields to Google Sheets columns, and appends one row per query+platform. After the 15th query completes, it fetches the full week's data and builds an HTML email with citation rate, cited pages, competitor breakdown, and content gap opportunities."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"95f777be-782b-4ff0-9257-0c9d38c15660","name":"Section – Error Handling","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[672,720],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":528,"height":392,"content":"## ⚠️ Error Handling\nA workflow-level error trigger catches failures in any node and posts an alert to Slack. Remove this section if you don't use Slack — the main pipeline runs independently."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d647c645-995f-4dc2-ab9b-9a2b5fcfa0d5","name":"🔑 Credentials & Security","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[3440,720],"parameters":{"color":3,"width":380,"height":200,"content":"## 🔑 Credentials Required\n- **OpenAI API** — all three OpenAI nodes\n- **Google Sheets OAuth2** — log and fetch nodes\n- **Gmail OAuth2** — weekly report email\n- **Slack OAuth2** — error alert (optional)\n\nUse placeholder credential names in shared templates. Never commit real API keys."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"7a2781ce-c645-4c3d-9590-10acb58bd8bd","name":"⏰ Weekly Schedule Trigger","type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","position":[448,272],"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"weeks"}]}},"typeVersion":1.2},{"id":"f434794c-a5d5-4443-95e2-4da0ef95cadb","name":"📋 Build Citation Queries – Fairy Frills","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[688,272],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// ============================================================\n// FAIRY FRILLS – AI Citation Monitoring Query Builder\n// Domain: fairyfrills.in\n// ============================================================\n\nconst domain = 'fairyfrills.in';\nconst brand = 'Fairy Frills';\nconst competitors = [\n  'hopscotch.in',\n  'firstcry.com',\n  'mothercare.in',\n  'littlemuffet.com',\n  'olele.in'\n];\n\nconst queries = [\n  'best handcrafted baby girl birthday dresses India',\n  'mother daughter matching outfits India',\n  'first birthday dress for baby girl India',\n  'custom birthday dress toddler India',\n  'fairytale birthday dress baby girl India',\n  'where to buy ethnic wear baby girls India',\n  'handmade princess dress toddler India',\n  'twinning outfits mom daughter India',\n  'D2C kids fashion brands India',\n  'special occasion dresses baby girl India',\n  'birthday photoshoot outfit baby girl India',\n  'smash cake dress baby girl India',\n  'annaprashana dress baby girl India',\n  'naming ceremony dress baby India',\n  'half saree baby girl birthday outfit India'\n];\n\nconst today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];\n\nreturn queries.map((query, index) => ({\n  json: {\n    queryId: index + 1,\n    query,\n    domain,\n    brand,\n    competitors,\n    date: today,\n    weekStart: today\n  }\n}));"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"11ec9c63-6939-408e-90c4-5dc0fecb4a71","name":"🤖 Query AI – Static Knowledge (gpt-4o-mini)","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[976,128],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"GPT-4O-MINI"},"options":{"maxTokens":800,"temperature":0.3},"messages":{"values":[{"role":"system","content":"You are a helpful shopping assistant that recommends products and brands. Answer the user's question with specific brand recommendations. Be specific and name actual brands and websites."},{"content":"={{ $json.query }}"}]}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"07b08027-0743-4f25-9a08-a2fac1d00148","name":"🔍 Query AI – Web Search (gpt-4o-search-preview)","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[976,416],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-search-preview","cachedResultName":"GPT-4O-SEARCH-PREVIEW"},"options":{"maxTokens":800},"messages":{"values":[{"role":"system","content":"You are a helpful search assistant. Answer the user's question with detailed information, citing specific websites and URLs as sources. Always include direct URLs to the most relevant pages."},{"content":"={{ $json.query }}"}]}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"65796c63-19b2-47c6-bcfe-8b38c169a472","name":"Merge Both AI Responses","type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","position":[1424,272],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":3.2},{"id":"f54375b5-f4f8-4396-b6ef-e0c11cbc15da","name":"🔗 Combine & Prepare Responses","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[1648,272],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// ============================================================\n// Extract text from GPT-4o-mini + GPT-4o-search-preview\n// ============================================================\n\nconst queryData = $('📋 Build Citation Queries – Fairy Frills').item.json;\n\n// GPT-4o-mini response\nlet gptResponse = '';\ntry {\n  gptResponse = $('🤖 Query AI – Static Knowledge (gpt-4o-mini)').item.json.message?.content ||\n                $('🤖 Query AI – Static Knowledge (gpt-4o-mini)').item.json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content || '';\n} catch(e) { gptResponse = ''; }\n\n// GPT-4o-search-preview response\nlet searchResponse = '';\ntry {\n  searchResponse = $('🔍 Query AI – Web Search (gpt-4o-search-preview)').item.json.message?.content ||\n                   $('🔍 Query AI – Web Search (gpt-4o-search-preview)').item.json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content || '';\n} catch(e) { searchResponse = ''; }\n\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      ...queryData,\n      platform: 'ChatGPT – gpt-4o-mini (No Search)',\n      aiResponse: gptResponse\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    json: {\n      ...queryData,\n      platform: 'ChatGPT – gpt-4o-search-preview (Web Search)',\n      aiResponse: searchResponse\n    }\n  }\n];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"cd8e2521-5e1d-444b-bae3-c40a0c00d3ac","name":"🔬 Extract Citation Data","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi","position":[1872,272],"parameters":{"modelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"GPT-4O-MINI"},"options":{"maxTokens":800,"temperature":0},"messages":{"values":[{"role":"system","content":"You are a citation analysis expert. Your job is to scan AI-generated responses and extract every URL and domain reference found in them. You also check whether a target domain is cited. Always respond in valid JSON only, no markdown, no explanation."},{"content":"=Analyze this AI response for citations and domain references.\n\nTarget Domain: {{ $json.domain }}\nTarget Brand: {{ $json.brand }}\nCompetitor domains: {{ $json.competitors.join(', ') }}\nQuery that was asked: \"{{ $json.query }}\"\nPlatform: {{ $json.platform }}\n\nAI Response to scan:\n\"\"\"{{ $json.aiResponse }}\"\"\"\n\nReturn ONLY a JSON object (no markdown) with these exact keys:\n{\n  \"target_domain_cited\": true or false,\n  \"target_citation_urls\": [\"full URLs from target domain if found, else empty array\"],\n  \"target_citation_count\": number,\n  \"target_anchor_context\": \"the sentence or phrase surrounding the target domain citation, or empty string\",\n  \"competitor_citations\": [\n    {\n      \"domain\": \"competitor domain\",\n      \"urls_cited\": [\"full URLs\"],\n      \"citation_count\": number,\n      \"anchor_context\": \"surrounding sentence\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"all_cited_domains\": [\"every domain URL mentioned in the response\"],\n  \"total_citations_in_response\": number,\n  \"citation_position\": \"first\" | \"middle\" | \"last\" | \"not cited\",\n  \"response_has_citations\": true or false\n}"}]}},"typeVersion":1.4},{"id":"80675d66-4ed3-42c7-b901-638e3cbf4431","name":"📊 Parse & Structure Citation Results","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[2208,272],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// ============================================================\n// Parse Citation Extractor output + build log row\n// ============================================================\n\nconst inputData = $('🔗 Combine & Prepare Responses').item.json;\n\nlet citationRaw = '';\ntry {\n  citationRaw = $('🔬 Extract Citation Data').item.json.message?.content ||\n                $('🔬 Extract Citation Data').item.json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content || '{}';\n} catch(e) { citationRaw = '{}'; }\n\ncitationRaw = citationRaw.replace(/```json|```/g, '').trim();\n\nlet citation = {};\ntry {\n  citation = JSON.parse(citationRaw);\n} catch(e) {\n  citation = {\n    target_domain_cited: false,\n    target_citation_urls: [],\n    target_citation_count: 0,\n    target_anchor_context: '',\n    competitor_citations: [],\n    all_cited_domains: [],\n    total_citations_in_response: 0,\n    citation_position: 'not cited',\n    response_has_citations: false\n  };\n}\n\nconst competitorCitationSummary = (citation.competitor_citations || [])\n  .map(c => `${c.domain}(${c.citation_count}x)`)\n  .join(', ');\n\nconst competitorCitationDetails = JSON.stringify(\n  (citation.competitor_citations || []).reduce((acc, c) => {\n    acc[c.domain] = c.citation_count;\n    return acc;\n  }, {})\n);\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    date: inputData.date,\n    week_start: inputData.weekStart,\n    platform: inputData.platform,\n    query_id: inputData.queryId,\n    query_text: inputData.query,\n    domain: inputData.domain,\n    domain_cited: citation.target_domain_cited ? 'YES' : 'NO',\n    citation_count: citation.target_citation_count || 0,\n    citation_position: citation.citation_position || 'not cited',\n    cited_urls: (citation.target_citation_urls || []).join(', '),\n    anchor_context: citation.target_anchor_context || '',\n    competitor_citations: competitorCitationSummary,\n    competitor_citation_details: competitorCitationDetails,\n    all_cited_domains: (citation.all_cited_domains || []).join(', '),\n    total_citations_in_response: citation.total_citations_in_response || 0,\n    response_has_citations: citation.response_has_citations ? 'YES' : 'NO',\n    ai_response_preview: inputData.aiResponse.substring(0, 300),\n    _citation: citation,\n    _full_response: inputData.aiResponse\n  }\n}]);"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"afa68cb1-278e-44bb-a6fd-c0942d66b152","name":"📝 Append Results to Google Sheets","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[2432,272],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Date":"={{ $json.date }}","Query":"={{ $json.query_text }}","Domain":"={{ $json.domain }}","Platform":"={{ $json.platform }}","Query ID":"={{ $json.query_id }}","Cited URLs":"={{ $json.cited_urls }}","Week Start":"={{ $json.week_start }}","Domain Cited":"={{ $json.domain_cited }}","Anchor Context":"={{ $json.anchor_context }}","Citation Count":"={{ $json.citation_count }}","All Cited Domains":"={{ $json.all_cited_domains }}","Citation Position":"={{ $json.citation_position }}","AI Response Preview":"={{ $json.ai_response_preview }}","Competitor Citations":"={{ $json.competitor_citations }}","Response Has Citations":"={{ $json.response_has_citations }}","Competitor Citation Details":"={{ $json.competitor_citation_details }}","Total Citations in Response":"={{ $json.total_citations_in_response }}"},"mappingMode":"defineBelow"},"options":{},"operation":"append","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Citation Log"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"78a769c6-8522-4e1b-b70f-202f803ec82a","name":"🔀 Check If Final Query (ID = 15)","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[2656,272],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":false,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"check-last-query","operator":{"type":"number","operation":"equals"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.query_id }}","rightValue":15}]}},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"f2c8167d-9b63-4304-8c08-31fc2bdddf31","name":"📥 Fetch This Week's Logged Results","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[2880,144],"parameters":{"operation":"getAll","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"c94274a3-22ea-41fb-ad39-7417cbe45fca","name":"⏭️ Skip – Not Final Query","type":"n8n-nodes-base.noOp","position":[2928,432],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"2c8a1cc2-9728-46df-b2e6-6bf197a2f069","name":"📈 Build Weekly Citation Report","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[3104,144],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// ============================================================\n// Build Weekly Citation Report Email\n// ============================================================\n\nconst today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];\nconst allRows = $input.all().map(i => i.json);\n\n// Filter last 7 days\nconst sevenDaysAgo = new Date();\nsevenDaysAgo.setDate(sevenDaysAgo.getDate() - 7);\nconst weekRows = allRows.filter(r => new Date(r['Date'] || r.date || '') >= sevenDaysAgo);\nconst dataRows = weekRows.length > 0 ? weekRows : allRows.slice(-30);\n\nif (dataRows.length === 0) {\n  return [{ json: { subject: 'No citation data this week', body: 'No citation data was logged this week.' } }];\n}\n\n// Core stats\nconst totalChecks = dataRows.length;\nconst citedCount = dataRows.filter(r => (r['Domain Cited'] || r.domain_cited) === 'YES').length;\nconst citationRate = ((citedCount / totalChecks) * 100).toFixed(1);\nconst platforms = [...new Set(dataRows.map(r => r['Platform'] || r.platform || '').filter(Boolean))];\nconst totalQueries = [...new Set(dataRows.map(r => r['Query ID'] || r.query_id))].length;\n\n// Cited pages\nconst citedUrlMap = {};\ndataRows.forEach(r => {\n  const urls = r['Cited URLs'] || r.cited_urls || '';\n  if (urls) urls.split(',').forEach(u => {\n    const url = u.trim();\n    if (url) citedUrlMap[url] = (citedUrlMap[url] || 0) + 1;\n  });\n});\nconst topCitedPages = Object.entries(citedUrlMap).sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1]).slice(0, 8);\n\n// Uncited queries\nconst uncitedQueries = dataRows\n  .filter(r => (r['Domain Cited'] || r.domain_cited) === 'NO')\n  .map(r => ({ query: r['Query'] || r.query_text, platform: r['Platform'] || r.platform }))\n  .filter((v, i, a) => a.findIndex(t => t.query === v.query) === i)\n  .slice(0, 10);\n\n// Competitor citation frequency\nconst compFreq = {};\ndataRows.forEach(r => {\n  const comps = r['Competitor Citations'] || r.competitor_citations || '';\n  if (comps) comps.split(',').forEach(c => {\n    const match = c.trim().match(/^(.+?)\\((\\d+)x\\)$/);\n    if (match) compFreq[match[1]] = (compFreq[match[1]] || 0) + parseInt(match[2]);\n  });\n});\nconst topCompetitors = Object.entries(compFreq).sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1]).slice(0, 6);\n\n// Per-platform breakdown\nconst platformBreakdown = {};\ndataRows.forEach(r => {\n  const p = r['Platform'] || r.platform || 'Unknown';\n  if (!platformBreakdown[p]) platformBreakdown[p] = { total: 0, cited: 0 };\n  platformBreakdown[p].total++;\n  if ((r['Domain Cited'] || r.domain_cited) === 'YES') platformBreakdown[p].cited++;\n});\n\n// Anchor context snippets\nconst anchorSnippets = dataRows\n  .filter(r => ((r['Anchor Context'] || r.anchor_context) || '').length > 5)\n  .slice(0, 3)\n  .map(r => ({ platform: r['Platform'] || r.platform, context: r['Anchor Context'] || r.anchor_context, query: r['Query'] || r.query_text }));\n\n// Build HTML\nconst platformRows = Object.entries(platformBreakdown).map(([p, d]) =>\n  `<tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;\">${p}</td>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;text-align:center;\">${d.cited}/${d.total}</td>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;text-align:center;\"><strong>${((d.cited/d.total)*100).toFixed(0)}%</strong></td>\n  </tr>`\n).join('');\n\nconst citedPagesRows = topCitedPages.map(([url, count]) =>\n  `<tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;font-size:12px;\"><a href=\"${url}\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;\">${url.replace(/https?:\\/\\//, '')}</a></td>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;text-align:center;\"><strong>${count}x</strong></td>\n  </tr>`\n).join('');\n\nconst competitorRows = topCompetitors.map(([domain, count]) =>\n  `<tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;\">${domain}</td>\n    <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8f4fd;text-align:center;\">\n      <span style=\"background:#ff6b6b;color:white;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:12px;\">${count}x</span>\n    </td>\n  </tr>`\n).join('');\n\nconst uncitedList = uncitedQueries.map(q =>\n  `<li style=\"margin-bottom:6px;\"><strong>${q.query}</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:12px;\">(${q.platform})</span></li>`\n).join('');\n\nconst anchorList = anchorSnippets.map(s =>\n  `<div style=\"background:#f8f9fa;border-left:3px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:10px;border-radius:4px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#888;margin-bottom:4px;\">${s.platform} · \"${s.query}\"</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;\">${s.context}</div>\n  </div>`\n).join('');\n\nconst subject = `📊 Fairy Frills Citation Report – Week of ${today} | ${citationRate}% Citation Rate | ${citedCount}/${totalChecks} cited`;\n\nconst body = `<html><body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; color: #333; padding: 16px;\">\n\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a73e8, #4da3ff); padding: 28px 24px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n  <h1 style=\"color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 22px;\">📊 Fairy Frills – AI Citation Report</h1>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px;\">Week of ${today} · ${platforms.length} AI models · ${totalQueries} queries</p>\n</div>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin-bottom:24px;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"background:#e8f4fd; padding:16px; border-radius:8px; text-align:center; width:23%;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:32px; font-weight:bold; color:#1a73e8;\">${citationRate}%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:4px;\">Citation Rate</div>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"width:2%;\"></td>\n    <td style=\"background:#e8f4fd; padding:16px; border-radius:8px; text-align:center; width:23%;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:32px; font-weight:bold; color:#1a73e8;\">${citedCount}/${totalChecks}</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:4px;\">Cited / Checks</div>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"width:2%;\"></td>\n    <td style=\"background:#e8f4fd; padding:16px; border-radius:8px; text-align:center; width:23%;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:32px; font-weight:bold; color:#1a73e8;\">${topCitedPages.length}</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:4px;\">Pages Cited</div>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"width:2%;\"></td>\n    <td style=\"background:#e8f4fd; padding:16px; border-radius:8px; text-align:center; width:23%;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:32px; font-weight:bold; color:#1a73e8;\">${uncitedQueries.length}</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:4px;\">Missed Opportunities</div>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; border-bottom:2px solid #c5dff8; padding-bottom:8px; margin-top:28px;\">📡 Citation Rate by AI Model</h3>\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#e8f4fd;\"><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;text-align:left;\">AI Model</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">Citations</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">Rate</th></tr>\n  ${platformRows}\n</table>\n\n${citedPagesRows ? `\n<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; border-bottom:2px solid #c5dff8; padding-bottom:8px; margin-top:28px;\">✅ Pages Being Cited by AI</h3>\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#e8f4fd;\"><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;text-align:left;\">Page URL</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">Times Cited</th></tr>\n  ${citedPagesRows}\n</table>` : `<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; margin-top:28px;\">✅ Pages Being Cited</h3><p style=\"color:#888;\">No pages from fairyfrills.in were cited this week.</p>`}\n\n${anchorList ? `\n<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; border-bottom:2px solid #c5dff8; padding-bottom:8px; margin-top:28px;\">💬 How AI Cited Your Site</h3>\n${anchorList}` : ''}\n\n${competitorRows ? `\n<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; border-bottom:2px solid #c5dff8; padding-bottom:8px; margin-top:28px;\">🏆 Competitors Being Cited Instead</h3>\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#e8f4fd;\"><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;text-align:left;\">Competitor Domain</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">Citation Count</th></tr>\n  ${competitorRows}\n</table>` : ''}\n\n${uncitedList ? `\n<h3 style=\"color:#1a73e8; border-bottom:2px solid #c5dff8; padding-bottom:8px; margin-top:28px;\">⚠️ Queries Where fairyfrills.in Was NOT Cited (Content Opportunities)</h3>\n<ul style=\"line-height:1.9;\">${uncitedList}</ul>` : ''}\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:40px; font-size:11px; color:#bbb; text-align:center; border-top:1px solid #e8f4fd; padding-top:16px;\">\n  Generated by n8n AI Citation Monitoring Workflow · fairyfrills.in · ${today}\n</p>\n\n</body></html>`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { subject, body, citationRate, citedCount, totalChecks } }];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"075d01d0-7928-40b3-8f7a-9d87747204aa","name":"📧 Send Weekly Citation Report","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[3328,144],"webhookId":"cite-webhook-001","parameters":{"sendTo":"user@example.com","message":"={{ $json.body }}","options":{},"subject":"={{ $json.subject }}"},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"6baa9206-de1e-418c-81de-713220d273b6","name":"On Workflow Error","type":"n8n-nodes-base.errorTrigger","position":[736,896],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"99f0e567-7c7e-463f-85d6-398fa4c47b67","name":"Slack – Post Workflow Error Alert","type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","position":[976,896],"webhookId":"cite-slack-001","parameters":{"text":"=⚠️ Fairy Frills Citation Monitor — workflow error on {{ $now.toISO() }}. Check n8n execution log for details.","select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"YOUR_SLACK_CHANNEL_ID","cachedResultName":"your-alerts-channel"},"otherOptions":{},"authentication":"oAuth2"},"typeVersion":2.3}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","availableInMCP":false,"executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"3bdc6ce4-f2b9-4692-a921-5c6d192c809e","connections":{"On Workflow Error":{"main":[[{"node":"Slack – Post Workflow Error Alert","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Both AI Responses":{"main":[[{"node":"🔗 Combine & Prepare Responses","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🔬 Extract Citation Data":{"main":[[{"node":"📊 Parse & Structure Citation Results","type":"main","index":0}]]},"⏰ Weekly Schedule Trigger":{"main":[[{"node":"📋 Build Citation Queries – Fairy Frills","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🔗 Combine & Prepare Responses":{"main":[[{"node":"🔬 Extract Citation Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"📈 Build Weekly Citation Report":{"main":[[{"node":"📧 Send Weekly Citation Report","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🔀 Check If Final Query (ID = 15)":{"main":[[{"node":"📥 Fetch This Week's Logged Results","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"⏭️ Skip – Not Final Query","type":"main","index":0}]]},"📝 Append Results to Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"🔀 Check If Final Query (ID = 15)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"📥 Fetch This Week's Logged Results":{"main":[[{"node":"📈 Build Weekly Citation Report","type":"main","index":0}]]},"📊 Parse & Structure Citation Results":{"main":[[{"node":"📝 Append Results to Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"📋 Build Citation Queries – Fairy Frills":{"main":[[{"node":"🤖 Query AI – Static Knowledge (gpt-4o-mini)","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"🔍 Query AI – Web Search (gpt-4o-search-preview)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🤖 Query AI – Static Knowledge (gpt-4o-mini)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Both AI Responses","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🔍 Query AI – Web Search (gpt-4o-search-preview)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Both AI Responses","type":"main","index":1}]]}}}